snippet.title: Dear Devere - Teaser
snippet.description:
I'm pleased to announce the release of Dear Devere. A visual novel told through a letter correspondence. Available on Itchio: https://katy133.itch.io/dear-devere

Voice acting by Chintarmanya Vivian ( https://phiaphox.wixsite.com/chintsy ) and Mike Young ( https://twitter.com/MikeYoungVO ).
